<h3>ACRIMAS work approach</h3>
<p><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,geneva; font-size: 11pt;">Large-scale incidents (man made and natural) inside and outside the EU require a coordinated response from crisis managers and first responders across Europe and with resources from all levels of government.</span></p>
